Title: S6 Ep. 245 Barry Nadler - Skills of the Future
Description:
Barry Nadler shared his five words that describe him. One of them is a phrase - positive deviant - what an interesting way to describe oneself. Tune in to hear what that means to him in the most positive way. His career path is quite the story and pretty entertaining. Star Wars is part of the story also. Fun!!
